283
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:05,177
Hinata Sakaguchi?

284
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:08,570
Dia salah seorang anak didik cikgu Shizu.

285
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:09,950
Oh...

286
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:13,750
